Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
loadBlackBoxNetlist(25.10)                          loadBlackBoxNetlist(25.10)

Name
       loadBlackBoxNetlist - Loads a netlist for a black box

Syntax
       loadBlackBoxNetlist

       [-help]

       <netlist>

       Loads  a netlist for a black box. You can use this command to incremen-
       tally load an updated netlist for a blackbox. You can use this  command
       before converting a blackbox to a fence.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description that includes the type and default
              information for each loadBlackBoxNetList parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man loadBlackBoxNetList

       <netlist>
              Specifies the netlist name. The netlist can  contain  more  than
              one  black box netlist, but it should not contain any non-black-
              box netlist.

              Data_type: string, required

Example
       The following command loads the netlist netlist_v1.

       loadBlackBoxNetlist netlist_v1

